WEBVTT

00:01.507 --> 00:02.776
I don't know anyone
that has ever made

00:02.777 --> 00:04.678
a long-distance
relationship work.

00:04.696 --> 00:06.656
But I can't stand
that I put you in this position,

00:06.681 --> 00:08.415
and the only way
I can see out of this

00:08.450 --> 00:11.035
is for you to go to Stanford.

00:11.069 --> 00:13.954
Come after me, Tanner.
That's what you're here for.

00:13.989 --> 00:15.239
You actually care about her.

00:15.290 --> 00:16.790
You think he didn't say
some things in there

00:16.825 --> 00:18.325
that got to me too?

00:18.359 --> 00:20.211
Well, I'm not bringing them up,
because right now,

00:20.245 --> 00:21.462
we need to stick together.

00:21.496 --> 00:23.363
Sticking together
means telling the truth.

00:23.381 --> 00:25.666
I can't stand
to see them come after you.

00:25.700 --> 00:26.884
You think I can't take it!

00:26.918 --> 00:28.252
Look, you're not listening
to me, okay?

00:28.303 --> 00:29.703
I can't take it!

00:29.721 --> 00:30.721
If all you want to do
is work with me,

00:30.755 --> 00:32.372
I can find a job
somewhere else.

00:32.390 --> 00:35.142
Scottie, that's not
all I want.

00:35.176 --> 00:36.176
Then say it.

00:36.210 --> 00:38.095
I want you in my life.

00:38.146 --> 00:39.513
I don't want her to go,

00:39.547 --> 00:41.381
and there's nothing
I can do about it.

00:41.399 --> 00:42.683
I finished my list.

00:42.717 --> 00:44.384
And?

00:44.402 --> 00:45.402
You're staying?

00:45.437 --> 00:48.939
Just try and stop me.

00:48.990 --> 00:53.077
This place has every
Harvard law student file ever.

00:53.111 --> 00:55.946
Do not touch
any of the files in here.

00:55.997 --> 00:58.666
Mike Ross--
he's not here.

