♪ everybody wanna know
how it feel ♪

05:20.845 --> 05:24.515
♪ everybody wanna see
what it's like ♪

05:24.549 --> 05:27.500
♪ living in a beehive
of your mind ♪

05:27.519 --> 05:30.905
♪ me and missus
so busy, busy making money ♪

